{
  "title": "tayanini Kongadavane cekecekele",
  "titleCh": "多納部落的形成",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "傳說最早到多納的是原住在「Taengelane」的聚落，由頭目家系Lawbwalate領其平民Laodathe家人，帶著頭目的狗Kaovatingi到「Kongadavane」打獵，回程在「Tathoane」休息，但Kaovatingi又自行跑回「Kongadavane」，並且不願再回去。獵人回到部落便向Lawbwalate家報告，並說明「Kongadavane」水源充足、獵物豐富、適合居住，建議乾脆遷徙居住，又邀請Pa’acengane家族同時遷移至多納，Taengelane家族因勢力薄弱，為避免被外族入侵，因此請Pa’acengane的勢力進入以自保，並請以Pa’acengane的頭目為共同頭目。",
      "ab": "sobilini babaka ko bowane, syaonga cekecekele ’ikay Kongadavane ka tali Taengelane. ko talyalalay Labwalate ka lameamece ko ka’olini Laodathe cocoaw. syatho ko athoini ki Labwalate Kawvatingi mwa Kongadavane walopo. ko ’abeini ka la’isasadra ’ikay Tathoane. makasi ki Kawvatingi ka lasivivi mwa Kongadavane, ikibakanga ’abee. ko walopo ka so’abeenga mwa ma’itikaykay Labwalatane.\r\n[===]\r\n’apobaka “Kongadavane ka madraw na acilay, madraw na bee, maagi’i ka ta’ikane, taongay mwa dryane ’aela.” mya. lawala mamaa tali Pa’acengane ’angese ’aela mwa Kongadavane. tali Taengelane ka isapawvikane maki’ecenge, patolo ni’isadra iti’ave namiya na baa mya. swalralranga tali Pa’acengane ko talyalalaini titalyalalay.",
      "order": "1",
